$!
$!------------------------------------------------------------------------------
$! SSL$RQST_CERT.COM - SSL Certificate Request procedure
$!------------------------------------------------------------------------------
$!
$ Verify = F$VERIFY (0)
$ Set NoOn
$ Set NoControl=Y
$!
$!------------------------------------------------------------------------------
$! Description 
$!------------------------------------------------------------------------------
$!
$! This procedure prompts the user through creating a Certificate Request.
$!
$! There are no parameters used.
